URL: 
	1. INCIDENTS 		- https://api.vistara.io/api/v2/tenants/{clientId}/incidents/{incidentId}/notes
	2. SERVICE REQUESTS - https://api.vistara.io/api/v2/tenants/{clientId}/serviceRequests/{serviceReqId}/notes

METHOD : POST

HEADERS :
	Authorization : Bearer {accessToken}
	Content-Type : application/json
	Accept : application/json

MANDATORY FEILDS : 
	1. description

EX: https://api.vistara.io/api/v2/tenants/client_93/incidents/{incidentId}/notes
	
Request:
{
  "description" : "this notes is created from api"
}

Response:
{
  "id" : 15,
  "subject" : "test notes"
}

Response Code: 200 OK